user.bio: It's not often that I drink beer... But when I do, I check in on Untappd!

beer.beer_description: Pale straw in colour with a clean crisp malty palate and a drying finish, our pilsner is triple hopped with saaz and nelson sauvin hops for the best of the old world and the new.
A light sunshine colour, this refreshing summer ale with hints of tropical fruits and pineapple on the nose and palate is noted for its delicacy rather than a robust distinctiveness.

items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 465 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower.
It's time for Summer! It's that time of year where you hit the beach and crack open your favorite Summer brew! That's at least 20 different Summer beers! Try 5 more for Level 5!

beer.beer_description: Bright golden in colour, our version of an American pale ale has bold upfront citrus & grapefruit aromas and flavours, perfectly balanced using specialty malts to create an all round beer for any weather.

This IPA is for the hop lover in you!
Hazy copper in colour with a rich aroma of tropical fruit and pine. Intense, hop explosion on the palate with hints of stone fruit and a crisp refreshing finish.
